OL,5,G1600 The Motorway
OL,6,     FOn the M5 near Birmingham,
OL,7,     FPatrollers Dave and Martyn shut
OL,8,     Fdown the motorway when a car on
OL,9,     Ffire gets dangerously out of
OL,10,     Fcontrol and is discovered to be
OL,11,     Fpacked with explosive contents.
OL,12,G1700 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,13,G     Speeders
OL,14,     FMultiple units race to catch a
OL,15,     Fgroup of potential car thieves.
OL,16,     FAnd police respond to a 999 call
OL,17,     Fabout a motorbike driving the
OL,18,     Fwrong way into oncoming traffic.
